                        <i class="fa-solid fa-star" data-value="5" style="pointer-events: none;"></i>
                    </span>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label><strong>Qualitative (Open-ended):</strong></label>
                    <div style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px;">
